    "transfer the pasta to the mini cocottes.\r\nadd the grated parmesan cheese to each cocotte.\r\nsprinkle the dried thyme, salt, and black pepper over the pasta and cheese.\r\nif using, sprinkle a pinch of crushed red pepper for added flavor.\r\ndot the top of each cocotte with a pat of unsalted butter.\r\nplace the cocottes in the preheated oven and bake for 4-6 minutes, until the cheese is melted and bubbly.\r\nremove from the oven and garnish with chopped fresh parsley.\r\nserve immediately and enjoy!",
